      <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What happens next?</h2>

      <p>We'll check you've submitted everything we need to progress your appeal.<br>We'll contact you once we've done this.</p>
      <p>You can find out more about the appeals process in the appeal a planning decision guidance.</p>

      <p class="govuk-body">
        <a data-cy="Feedback-Page-Body" href="https://forms.office.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=mN94WIhvq0iTIpmM5VcIjVqzqAxXAi1LghAWTH6Y3OJUOFg4UFdEUThGTlU3S0hFUTlERVYwMVRLTy4u" class="govuk-link">What did you
          think of this service?</a> (takes 2 minutes)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <input type="hidden" name="appealId" value="{{ appealId }}" data-cy="submission-information-appeal-id" />
{% endblock %}
